'''''The Official Star Wars Technical Journal''''' was published by [[Starlog Communications International]] in three volumes from [[1993]] to [[1994]]. These were compiled into a [[Star Wars Technical Journal|paperback and a hardcover volume]] in [[1995]] (the hardcover re-released in [[1997]]) and a [[Star Wars Technical Journal Collector's Edition|collector's edition]] in [[1996]].

